    %% Tracing flows
    TR_kserve -->|OTLP/gRPC| Collector
    TR_dsp -->|OTLP/gRPC| Collector
    TR_epp -->|OTLP/gRPC| Collector
    TR_guardrails -->|OTLP/gRPC| Collector
